{"tid":1632621,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"吐露港爆呔...","createTime":"2019-10-06T19:00:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T01:32:43.000Z","uid":146418,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"12317018bc700b93f0becd7e7733802f07156eba","tid":1632621,"uid":146418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:00:28.000Z","msg":"事源上星期有晚凌晨我係大埔出吐露港<br />\n點知一出到吐露港左後邊呔就中左粒直徑約1-2cm既鐵釘爆左呔（都唔緊要可能自己黑仔無辦法）<br />\n埋左邊後都唔夠三分鐘 有個拖車就閃住燈黎左我後邊問我需唔需要幫手（其實會唔會咁啱得咁橋？）<br />\n自己未試過呢個情況 唔熟價 收左我$850淨換後備呔（只安裝）呔係自己既<br />\n諗左幾日同朋友傾過都覺得成件事太巧合 你地點睇？<br />\n換完仲要俾左張卡片我<br />\n可能我多心 釘有冇機會係拖車佬放？搏生意？<br />\n[url]<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1c8q3Hx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1c8q3Hx.png&h=1971705c&s={SIZE}\" />[/url]"},{"pid":"b7bb8352f210ef4dff1677273d07bf17a91d5b62","tid":1632621,"uid":27112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:03:33.000Z","msg":"咁似林雪爆你呔再出嚟幫手收錢嘅劇情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fc1c274894abd468d3e52ea6f117aa95979e659","tid":1632621,"uid":146418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7bb8352f210ef4dff1677273d07bf17a91d5b62","tid":1632621,"uid":27112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:03:33.000Z","msg":"咁似林雪爆你呔再出嚟幫手收錢嘅劇情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:06:50.000Z","msg":"係唔係林雪劇情我就唔清楚 不過我條米仔呔就咁炸左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再跟手換左Goodyear F1A5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cc086e825f8b4d4316c411adb0ea42165a46314","tid":1632621,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T00:58:00.000Z","msg":"平時銀包袋兩三百蚊咋喎<br />\n無啦啦 $850 無錢俾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae40480acb1dab3dbe7b44689f8b2b3b0298f15e","tid":1632621,"uid":106290,"like":4,"dislike":0,